question: Lily is required to submit a 282-page thesis. She already finished writing 1/3 of the thesis. How many pages does she have left to write?
answer:
Lily has already written 1/3 of the thesis which is 282 pages*1/3 = <<282*1/3=94>>94 pages.
So, she still needs to write 282 pages - 94 pages = <<282-94=188>>188 pages.
#### 188
